# 🌐 Networking Theory

## Structured Network Troubleshooting

Professional troubleshooting follows a logical sequence instead of guessing.

### Step 1

Verify Network Interface

```bash
ip addr
```

---

### Step 2

Verify Routing Table

```bash
ip route
```

---

### Step 3

Test Gateway Connectivity

```bash
ping <gateway-ip>
```

---

### Step 4

Test Internet Connectivity

```bash
ping 8.8.8.8
```

---

### Step 5

Test DNS Resolution

```bash
nslookup google.com
```

---

### Step 6

Trace Network Path

```bash
tracepath google.com
```

