# Real World Scenario

## Situation

A user reports that the company application is running very slowly.

Investigation:

CPU usage is consistently above 95%.

Memory usage remains below 40%.

Disk usage is normal.

Using:

```bash
top
```

the administrator identifies a process consuming excessive CPU resources.

After further investigation, the problematic application is restarted.

System performance returns to normal.

